column2:
"Thanks to <%me>, we were
able to complete the quest. Thank you very much."
"Thank you for helping me! I'm very grateful!"
"I hope we can play again soon~! Oh, Okawa, are you working tomorrow?"
"Huh...? T-that's personal information, don't talk about it out in the open."
"Oh, so it is! I-I'm sorry! I was being careless!"
"Anyway, all of our orders have been completed. I really enjoyed this!"

"<%me>, thank you so much
for taking our silly orders."
